programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb…

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: Marrying Mr Perfect
programme.desc: Winnie is dumped by her boyfriend in her late twenties and unknowingly meets Koo, a ruthless tycoon in business and a playboy. Koo temporarily switches identities with his driver for security reason and falls for Winnie as she is the first girl to love him for who he is. What will happen when Winnie know Koo’s real identity?

programme.title: Midnight Diner
programme.desc: A small restaurant in Shanghai is open only from midnight to early morning. The chef has no menu but will create something unique for each customer. Through the years, people come to the Midnight Diner to share their stories, taste the chef’s delicious food and leave feeling comforted and fulfilled.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: Loving You
programme.desc: A bad-tempered, womanizing cop who always neglects his wife is shot in the head as he hunts down a drug dealer. Though he miraculously survives, he must depend on his wife to nurse him back to health. During the recovery, he begins to re-evaluate his life and repair the damages of his broken marriage.

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Gambler
programme.desc: Manfred and Flora are gambling addicts who have come across each other a few times at the casino, but do not leave impression on each other until they both suffer heavy losses and are held hostage by the loan sharks in Macau. They find themselves falling in love, and decide to get married when they come back to Hong Kong.

programme.title: Come Back Home
programme.desc: In a chilly winter, De and his family goes on a self-drive tour to Changbai Mountain. The holiday turns tragic when De’s eight-year-old son goes missing. He seeks help from the local police but is unable to find his son. Though the golden hour has passed, De and the rescue team insist on continuing the search. Can they finally rescue the boy?

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Choi’s actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: Death Notice
programme.desc: A serial killer leaves death notices in a city, stating when, how and who he will murder. Even if the victims report it to the police and receive protection, the killer can still break through and execute them. While the police sets up a special task force in response, they expose an even bigger conspiracy behind.

programme.title: Miao Miao
programme.desc: Miao Miao is an awkward young beauty who nevertheless enchants her outgoing classmate Xiao Ai. As Xiao Ai’s feelings for Miao Miao grows from friendship to something more, Miao Miao discovers her own burgeoning attraction to a sullen CD store owner, and quietly pursues him.

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: iGirl
programme.desc: Evan, Johnny, and Irwin are best friends. All three of them get dumped by their girlfriends one day and decide to find three robotic substitutes, the iGirls, as their new girlfriends. However, as time goes by, Evan finds himself falling in love with his iGirl…

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Eva’s mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mother’s wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Eva’s heart?

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of “The Way We Dance” features the plight of Hong Kong’s grassroots performing artists as they fight against the government’s plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: The Fatal Raid
programme.desc: Twenty years after a deadly bloodbath between the Hong Kong Police and Macau gangsters, Madam Fong, the surviving team member, leads a new squad of four policewomen across borders to pursue young anarchists terrorizing Macau in a mission to protect the Hong Kong Police’s Deputy Chief Commissioner.

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: Undercover Hidden Dragon
programme.desc: In this hilarious comedy, Fat is a gangster who suffers from amnesia. Believing that he is actually an undercover policeman, Fat attempts to arrest gang leader Big Bro, but instead becomes the gangsters’ best ally. To complicate matters further, a gangster named Wind, who looks exactly like Fat, starts a turf war with Big Bro.

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Till We Meet Again
programme.desc: Ng Ka Wai is hoping that he will see his loving mother Mui again one day. Mui has apparently been avoiding her son for over a decade while Wai is suffering from depression and panic disorder. When his lost memory suddenly returns, he recalls what he has done to his mother - an unforgivable sin leading to the 10-year separation.

programme.title: Ashes of Time Redux
programme.desc: After his beloved woman married his brother, Ou Yang Feng moves to the desert to run an inn and becomes a killer agent. He makes acquaintance of different people with their different stories ... The movie is the winner of the 1st Hong Kong Film Critics Society Awards for Best Film, Best Director, Best Screenplay and Best Actor (Leslie Cheung).

programme.title: Love at First Lie
programme.desc: An ordinary, cheerful and kind-hearted girl Bao, meets a troubled rich guy Edward by chance one summer. To ruin his father’s remarriage plans, Edward hires Bao and her friend to sabotage the wedding and that is how Bao and Edward meet and fall in love. All seems well for the sweet couple until their love quickly takes an unexpected turn…

programme.title: My School Mate, The Barbarian
programme.desc: Edward attends a new school which has a reputation for fighting. Student leader Stone, befriends Edward, but their friendship is tested when a local triad leader discovers that Edward comes from a wealthy family.

programme.title: Everything is Unknown
programme.desc: Pan Yi Ming receives his father's will stating that he must attend his funeral at home to claim the huge inheritance. When he returns home, he encounters his ex-girlfriend, her husband Hua Qi and his daughter whom he has never met. When Pan discovers that his daughter is being abused by Hua, he vows to save her but eventually fall into their trap…

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: In this prequel, the secrets of “Infernal Affairs” are revealed - the resentment between police superintendent Wong and crime boss Sam, as well as the beginning of the parallel fates of the two moles, Yan and Ming. The keys lie in the hands of Sam's wife, a ruthless kingpin and a righteous cop.

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killer’s mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened…

programme.title: Lion Rock
programme.desc: Based on the true story of David Ki, one of Asia’s top rock climbers who lost everything when a motorcycle accident crippled him. Rather than succumbing to his fate, David found a way of scaling the dizzying peaks again by becoming a wheelchair-bound athlete and soon reached the peak of Lion Rock!

programme.title: Mad Fate
programme.desc: A Master fortune teller predicts that Tung, a born psychopath, will be imprisoned for murder and tries to change his fate. A veteran detective believes Tung is a psychopathic serial killer after witnessing him kill a cat, and pursues him relentlessly. Can the Master change Tung’s mad fate?

programme.title: Adventure of the King
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor Zhengde flees the palace to see the world after his mother orders him to marry an ugly princess. He disguises as a commoner and escapes with his advisors, but a gambling mishap causes them to part ways and Zhengde lost all his money. Phoenix, the owner of Lung Fung Inn, takes him in out of pity, and thus begins his new adventure...

programme.title: Ready O/R Knot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi have been together for five years since they first met in a wedding banquet, but marriage soon becomes a challenge to their relationship. Heidi sees marriage as a testimony of their love, while Guy sees it as doomsday. Can the couple resolve their conflict? Are they ready or not?

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Set in 2020 during the outbreak of COVID-19, the movie features interconnected stories of three women's lives as they navigate the uncertain future amongst their respective friends and families. From the struggles at home to challenges in relationships and conflicts at work, these three women rise with strength when faced with plights unknown.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Coffin Homes
programme.desc: Three bizarre tales intertwine in this horror satire set against the housing crisis of Hong Kong, where soaring property prices have driven dwellers to take every insane effort necessary to secure a cramped space, even if it means sharing the same roof with the dead!

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the club’s top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenix’s (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

Lalu mereka ditolong Hadi hingga bisa menemukan pamannya. Tetapi kemudian mereka mengalami kecelakaan yanga membuat pamannya tewas, sementara mereka bertiga jadi cacat seperti gagu, pincang dan buta. Zainal, anak seorang pemilik perusahaan diusir ayahnya saat hendak menolong Bastian, anak seorang narapidana. Mereka berjuang bersama sampai akhirnya terlibat dalam komplotan penyelundup emas. Indra, kekasih Selvy, berusaha merebut Tika dari Rhoma Irama, sedangkan Beny Compo, kakak Selvy, berusaha menghancurkan karir musik Rhoma Irama sebagai pelampiasan dendam

Kokom (Kompilasi Komedi)
programme.desc: Program yang berisikan kompilasi video-video lucu yang viral di sosial media.

programme.title: Terang Kasih
programme.desc: Siraman rohani Kristen yang berkaitan dengan kehidupan untuk mendekatkan diri kepada Tuhan Yesus Kristus. Program ini akan dibagi menjadi beberapa bagian, antara lain kesaksian, renungan, serta konseling yang akan dipandu oleh dua orang host

programme.title: Unik Enak
programme.desc: Sebuah program kompilasi masakan-masakan unik yang ada didunia. Baik itu dilihat dari cara memasak hingga bahan baku yang digunakan serta memberikan informasi seputar dunia masak-memasak.

programme.title: Seru! (Semua Harus Tau)
programme.desc: Program informasi dokumenter yang menyajikan berbagai informasi disertai dengan pemaparannya. Program ini membahas berbagai hal yang seru dan unik yang dilihat dari berbagai sisi serta dipaparkan oleh VO (Voice Over). Selain menghibur, program ini juga kaya akan pengetahuan sehingga akan menambah banyak wawasan bagi pemirsa.

programme.title: Boba (Bombastis Banget)
programme.desc: BOBA (BOMBASTIS BANGET) merupakan program yang berisi informasi ringan yang menyajikan video-video bombastis yang viral, lucu, dan unik dari sosial media. Bisa berupa video kejadian yang tidak biasa ataupun video yang sedang viral. Video-video tersebut akan dikomentari dengan menggunakan VO (voice over) dan dikemas dengan editing yang kekinian.

programme.title: Superbook
programme.desc: Animasi religi kristen yang menceritakan petualangan seru Chris dan Joy, bersama robot mereka Gizmo. Melalui sebuah alat bernama Superbook, mereka bertiga mampu menjelajah lorong waktu, bertemu dengan tokoh-tokoh Alkitab, dan menjadi saksi mata sejarah. Melalui petualangan mereka inilah, Superbook membawa pesan Alkitab kepada generasi anak-anak di era digital.

programme.title: Metal Cardbot
programme.desc: Dahulu kala, terdapat sebuah planet bernama Machina dimana Metal Cardbots tinggal. Suatu ketika, planet ini tiba-tiba meledak dan memaksa semua penghuninya untuk hidup di Bumi. Agar tidak menarik perhatian makhluk Bumi, Cardbots menyamar sebagai kendaraan sehari-hari. Hingga suatu hari, seorang anak sekolah dasar yang bernama Jun secara tidak sengaja menemukan Metal Breath, dengan Metal Breath tersebut dia bisa menangkap dan menyalakan Cardbots dengan kemampuan yang berbeda.

programme.title: Pokemon Horizons
programme.desc: Petualangan seru dengan karakter karakter baru yang berlatar di dunia Pokémon yang sudah dikenal dan menyenangkan Baik Liko maupun Roy memiliki benda benda misterius yang masing masing sebuah liontin dan Poké Ball yang tampak unik tetapi untuk mengungkap makna benda benda tersebut Liko harus mengambil langkah pertama yang berani Sepanjang perjalanan Liko dan Roy bertemu Friede Kapten Pikachu, dan Amethio Dengan dunia Pokémon yang luas sebagai panggung mereka Liko dan Roy memulai petualangan baru mereka Pertemuan dan takdir apa yang akan terjadi Di sinilah kisah petualangan baru dan penemuan apa yang benar benar penting dimulai

programme.title: Ultraman Arc
programme.desc: Ultraman Arc bercerita tentang Yuma Hize yang bergabung ke Pusat Investigasi dan Pencegahan Kaiju Ilmiah (SKIP). Dalam sebuah tugas, secara tidak sengaja Yuma Hize bergabung dengan raksasa cahaya dari galaksi yang jauh dan bertransformasi menjadi Ultraman Arc.

programme.title: Beyblade X
programme.desc: Beyblade X mengikuti kisah Robin Kazami, seorang Blader muda yang ditinggalkan timnya setelah kekalahan telak. Dia kemudian bertemu dengan Jaxon Cross, mantan juara Beyblade, dan mereka berdua membentuk tim baru bernama Tim Persona. Bersama dengan anggota ketiga tim, Multi Nana-iro, mereka bercita-cita untuk mencapai puncak liga Beyblade X.

programme.title: Cai Yoo (Cerita Anak Indonesia Yoo Yoo Yoo)
programme.desc: Program hiburan yang edukatif yang disajikan bagi penonton anak-anak, dipandu oleh seorang host yang akan mendatangi sekolah-sekolah untuk mengajak siswa bermain sambil belajar bersama. Program ini akan menampilkan praktik sains dari kakak Ilmuwan, pertunjukan dongeng, hingga pertunjukan bakat siswa seperti menyanyi, menari, berolahraga, dll. Pada setiap bagian program terdapat pembelajaran bagi siswa yang dikemas lebih menyenangkan.

programme.title: Doremi Dalimi
programme.desc: Dalimi yang penyayang selalu peduli dengan semua orang di sekitarnya, mulai dari Ayahnya, Ibunya, teman-temannya, kakeknya, adiknya, dan anjing peliharaan keluarga Milky. Setiap episodenya, kita akan mengikuti kehidupan sehari-hari Dalimi bersama orang tersayang.

programme.title: Super Wings
programme.desc: Pengantaran paket oleh Jett yang akan ditemani oleh super wings lainnya yang juga bisa berubah menjadi robot untuk memudahkan mereka dalam mengantarkan paket untuk anak-anak di seluruh dunia mulai dari pengantaran yang ringan sampai pengantaran yang sangat berat.

programme.title: Bola Kampung
programme.desc: Cerita ini berlatar di Kampung Gong Lechar di daerah Pohon Bambu. Berkisah tentang sekelompok remaja yang memiliki hasrat besar terhadap sepak bola untuk bersenang-senang. Kemudian kepala sekolah, Pak Doud, dan pelatih yang baru diangkat, Pak Abdul Rahman, memutuskan untuk membentuk tim sepak bola yang akan mewakili mereka dalam kompetisi antar sekolah. Iwan memimpin tim dalam perjuangannya menjadi tim terbaik di tingkat kabupaten. Sayangnya, mimpi Iwan ditentang oleh ayahnya, Azman, karena ayahnya tidak ingin Iwan menjadi sepertinya yang memiliki nasib tragis sehingga karir sepak bolanya tercoreng. Namun dengan dukungan teman-temannya, Azizul dan Sabok, Iwan berhasil mengatasi masalah dan muncul sebagai tulang punggung tim. Dengan kebersamaan, tim berusaha untuk mengatasi tantangan yang menghadang demi mencapai impiannya.

programme.title: Makan Mulu
programme.desc: Makan Mulu merupakan program yang menyajikan berbagai referensi kuliner serta jajanan yang kekinian, dan menjelajah tempat-tempat kuliner yang unik dan viral. Perjalanan ini tambah seru karena beragam kuliner dan lokasinya akan di review oleh seorang Food Vloger/Chef/Food Expert yang seru dan ekspresif.

programme.title: Skena
programme.desc: SKENA (Sekolah Kece Penuh Warna) merupakan program variety show yang menampilkan berbagai bakat unggulan dari siswa-siswi di sekolah tersebut. Selain ini, program ini juga menampilkan bintang tamu rahasia di setiap sekolahnya. Program ini akan dipandu oleh seorang host yang lucu, seru dan tentunya bisa bonding dengan anak SMP dan SMA.

programme.title: The Smurfs
programme.desc: Di tengah hutan belantara, terdapat desa rahasia dihuni oleh sekelompok makhluk kecil berwarna biru yang dipimpin oleh Papa Smurf. Para Smurf tinggal di rumah berbentuk jamur dan hidup dengan damai. Namun, kedatangan penyihir jahat Gargamel dan kucingnya, Azrael, merusak kedamaian desa tersebut. Sehingga para Smurf harus mencari cara agar tidak ditangkap oleh Gargamel dan Azrael.

programme.title: Pj Masks
programme.desc: Serial animasi ini berkisah tentang tiga anak normal yang berkegiatan pada siang hari. Namun pada malam hari, mereka akan menjadi pahlawan yang menggunakan topeng. Biasanya, masalah itu terjadi pada siang hari saat mereka sekolah. Dan tugas mereka, menyelesaikan masalah itu pada malam harinya. Akan ada banyak ide dan strategi yang mereka gunakan dalam memecahkan masalah. Mereka sangat mengenali kekuatan dan kelemahan masing-masing. Mereka memutuskan beraksi pada malam hari karena menganggap waktu tidur merupakan waktu yang tepat untuk memerangi kejahatan.

programme.title: Tobot Daedo'S Heroes
programme.desc: Pasukan robot jahat telah menghilang dari Kota Daedo. Para Tobot tidak lagi dibutuhkan untuk menyelamatkan Kota Daedo, dan mereka perlahan menghilang sebagai legenda urban belaka. Setelah banyak teman mereka pergi ke kota yang berbeda, Ryan, Kory, dan Dylan sekarang menjadi siswa kelas lima. Franklin dan Limo menjalankan bengkel mekanik bersama-sama dengan damai, tetapi mereka kembali mencari para Tobot untuk menghentikan robot jahat baru yang telah muncul di Kota Daedo.

programme.title: Riseman
programme.desc: Serial animasi dengan tokoh utama seorang putra pemilik toko pangsit terkenal di Zero City bernama Scoot. Suatu hari saat melakukan pengiriman makanan, Scoot tanpa sengaja mengambil Geostone yang jatuh dari langit. Albert yang merupakan seorang ilmuwan, menciptakan monster baru agar lebih banyak kaiju yang diciptakannya. Dia berencana untuk mendapatkan Geostone tersebut, sehingga mengirimkan kaiju ke bumi. Khawatir bahwa bumi dalam bahaya dari monster luar angkasa tersebut, V seorang polisi luar angkasa melihat keberanian Scoot dalam mempertahankan desanya kemudian memberikan Scoot sebuah Rise Spark yang bisa merubahnya menjadi Riseman. Scoot bertarung melawan berbagai monster yang ingin menghancurkan bumi untuk mengambil Geostone.

programme.title: Riko The Series
programme.desc: Menceritakan keseharian seorang anak yang bernama Riko berusia 8 tahun Dia adalah anak yang pintar rajin dan aktif Kesehariannya menjadi sebuah petualangan bagi Riko dan sahabatnya Q 110 untuk menemukan dan mempelajari hal hal disekitarnya Dalam petualangannya Ia juga sering menemukan hal hal baru yang kemudian hal hal itu dijelaskan oleh Q 110 Dalam penjelasan Q 110 Riko mempelajari banyak pengetahuan soal ilmuan ilmuan muslim dari penjuru dunia kehebatan Allah sang maha pencipta dan tentunya banyak hal lainya

programme.title: Tendangan Halilintar
programme.desc: Berkisah tentang pertandingan sepanjang masa antara Tim Garuda yang beranggotakan Akbar, Abbas, Hafiz, Marco dan Tito melawan Alvan, Peter, Kevin, Igor dan Bari yang tergabung dalam Tim Super untuk bisa menjadi pemenang.

programme.title: Boboiboy
programme.desc: Sebuah program animasi yang mengisahkan Boboiboy dan teman-temannya yakni Gopal, Ying, dan Yaya yang masing-masing memiliki kekuatan super. Dengan kekuatan yang dimiliki mereka mencegah Adu Du mencuri biji kakao Tok Aba yang digunakan sebagai sumber energi. Selain itu, Boboiboy dan teman-temannya menjadi pahlawan super dalam menumpas kejahatan dan menjaga kedamaian Bumi.

programme.title: Ejen Ali
programme.desc: Serial animasi dengan tokoh utama bernama Ali yang tidak sengaja menjadi agen Meta Advance Tactical Agency (MATA). Ali membuktikan diri bahwa Ia mampu menjadi agen MATA dan mengalahkan musuh bersama Alicia dan Paman bakar

programme.title: Boba (Bombastis Banget)
programme.desc: BOBA (BOMBASTIS BANGET) merupakan program yang berisi informasi ringan yang menyajikan video-video bombastis yang viral, lucu, dan unik dari sosial media. Bisa berupa video kejadian yang tidak biasa ataupun video yang sedang viral. Video-video tersebut akan dikomentari dengan menggunakan VO (voice over) dan dikemas dengan editing yang kekinian.

programme.title: Check In (Check Informasi)
programme.desc: Program yang menyajikan fakta-fakta unik tentang fenomena serta isu terkini yang terjadi di dunia melalui video-video yang bersumber dari media sosial dan dipaparkan oleh Voice Over (VO) yang unik.
